# Fly Time Client Questions

Keep this file for backend/client decisions that are blocked on business or provider details.

## Admin Auth

- Confirm admin login method:
  - Supabase email/password
  - Supabase magic link/OTP
  - external provider such as Google Workspace
- Confirm roles needed beyond `admin` and `editor`.
- Confirm whether admin must support multi-branch/team access later.

## Booking Form

- Confirm exact fields for trip booking/enquiry.
- Confirm whether payment is enquiry-only, pay-later, or online payment.
- Confirm whether users receive automatic confirmation emails.

## Flight API

- Provider name and documentation URL.
- Sandbox API keys and auth method.
- Required search fields.
- Rate limits.
- Whether we only show quotes or also create bookings/tickets.

## Hotel API

- Provider name and documentation URL.
- Sandbox API keys and auth method.
- Required search fields.
- Room/guest child-age rules.
- Whether hotel booking is live booking or enquiry-only.

## Transport API

- Provider name and documentation URL if there is one.
- Required enquiry fields.
- Vehicle categories and pricing rules.

## Media And Email

- Choose Cloudinary or ImageKit as primary media provider.
- Confirm Resend or another transactional email provider.
- Confirm notification recipient email for admin enquiries.

